---
title: Charred Garlic-Lime Chicken with Avocado Salsa Verde and Spiced Honey-Butter Corn
description: Underneath those papery husks, tomatillos are one of summer’s most wonderful tomato varieties. After a quick char under the broiler, they become the star of our avocado salsa verde. We’d say it’s our favourite condiment, but that honey- butter might just take the cake!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/charred-garlic-lime-chicken-cf9d79e8.jpg
